title: KUNMI Women's Ripped Skinny Slim Fit Jeans Frayed Distressed Stretchy Denim Pants
description: Comes in a stretchable denim with a classic 5-pocket design, 4-button front, and zip-fly closure.
Stretchy, Skinny Leg, Split Ankles, Front Fading & Whiskering.

These jeans comes in a faded, dark, and medium blue wash with whiskering, distress around the knee area. Its staggered raw hem gives it a hip edge that's both trendy and modern. Pairs well with white tees or your favorite pair of booties.

Sits just above the natural waistline as it tapers down the leg creating a figure-flattering silhouette that's perfect for dressing up or down. Made with smooth stretch denim that allows you to move with ease without bagging out after each wear.
Machine Wash Cold inside out, Tumble Dry Low. Due to the different displays of the computers, the color of the real item may be a little different from the picture shown.
